{
  "texts": [
    "All variants of Flan-T5 have a 512-token context length limit.• ChatGLM [172]: ChatGLM is an open-source bilingual dialogue LLM that supports both Chinese and English, based on the General Language Model (GLM) [172] with the prefix decoder architecture.",
    "The team released the second version ChatGLM2 and the third version ChatGLM3 in June 2023 and October 2023, respectively.",
    "Note that ChatGLM2 and ChatGLM3 have replaced the model architecture with a casual encoder.",
    "All three versions of open-source ChatGLM have a parameter scale of 6B.",
    "As for the context length, ChatGLM-6B supports 2K tokens while ChatGLM2-6B can cover 32K tokens at one time."
  ]
}